what was done: temple filler to fill out loss of volume and lift the outer corners of the eyes. in my opinion worked better then Botox for that “fox eye” look. Jawline filler to slim and define the jawline & a little bit of chin filler for facial balance. I was unaware of how much a difference it makes to keep your face looking proportionate! Obsessed! 🤍
